headline: Aisle hopping: Why major food and beverage brands are entering new parts of the grocery store
summary: Nestlé, Kraft Heinz and J.M. Smucker are among the CPG giants leveraging the brand equity of well-known products to expand into different categories, boost recognition and grow sales.
